# IntakeAI 🏥

> AI-powered bilingual patient intake automation for private practice doctors.
> Patients fill out a smart intake form → AI instantly generates a structured clinical summary for the doctor.

---

## What Is IntakeAI?

IntakeAI eliminates the #1 administrative burden in private medical practices: manual patient intake. Instead of paper forms and staff re-entering data, patients complete a digital intake form (in English or Spanish), and the AI instantly generates a physician-ready clinical summary — before the appointment even starts.

**Built for:** Independent family practice doctors in the US, with a focus on bilingual (English/Spanish) practices in Texas, Florida, California, and the Southwest.

---

## The Problem We Solve

| Without IntakeAI | With IntakeAI |
|---|---|
| Paper or PDF intake forms | Smart digital form on any device |
| Staff manually entering patient data | AI processes and structures data instantly |
| Doctor reads raw form during visit | Doctor receives structured clinical summary |
| English-only intake at most practices | Full English + Spanish support |
| No integration with clinical workflow | EHR-ready export (Phase 2) |

