## Business Documents

### HIPAA Business Associate Agreement
**File:** `IntakeAI_BAA_Template.docx`

Full 9-section BAA template covering:
- Permitted uses and disclosures of PHI
- Required security safeguards (AES-256, TLS, MFA, RBAC, audit logs)
- Subcontractor BAA requirements (Supabase, AWS, Anthropic listed)
- Breach notification requirements (60-day rule)
- Term, termination, and data destruction
- Indemnification and governing law
- Dual signature blocks

> ⚠️ Have a healthcare attorney review before use. Fill in your state in Section 8.3.

---

### Supabase Database Schema
**File:** `intakeai_schema.sql`

HIPAA-compliant PostgreSQL schema for Supabase. Includes:

| Table | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `practices` | Each medical practice (tenant) |
| `providers` | Doctors and staff within a practice |
| `patients` | Patient demographics (PHI) |
| `appointments` | Scheduled visits |
| `intake_forms` | Raw intake form submissions |
| `clinical_summaries` | AI-generated summaries (auditable) |
| `audit_log` | HIPAA-required access log (6-year retention) |
| `intake_tokens` | Secure one-time patient form links (48hr expiry) |

All tables have Row Level Security (RLS) enabled. Providers only see their own practice's data.

