## HIPAA Compliance Checklist

Before going live with real patient data:

- [ ] Sign BAA with **Supabase** (available on Pro plan)
- [ ] Sign BAA with **Anthropic** — email privacy@anthropic.com
- [ ] Sign BAA with **AWS** (if using any AWS services)
- [ ] Prepare your own **BAA template** to give to each practice (use `IntakeAI_BAA_Template.docx`)
- [ ] Enable **MFA** on all provider accounts
- [ ] Configure **session timeouts** (15 min idle)
- [ ] Set up **audit logging** (use `audit_log` table)
- [ ] Publish **Privacy Policy** and **Terms of Service**
- [ ] Publish **HIPAA Notice of Privacy Practices**
- [ ] Run annual **security risk assessment**

