## Go-To-Market Strategy

### Phase 1 — Seed (Year 1, 2025)
- Direct outreach to 50 independent practices in Austin / Pflugerville / Round Rock
- Free 30-day trials to close first 10 customers
- Focus: solo family practice doctors
- Target: 25 paying practices, $7.5K MRR

### Phase 2 — Growth (Year 2, 2026)
- EHR integrations (Epic, Athenahealth, DrChrono)
- Referral program
- Group practice and enterprise tiers
- Target: 95 practices, $41.7K MRR

### Phase 3 — Scale (Year 3, 2027)
- Series A fundraise (~$4M)
- Sales team of 4 reps
- White-label product for medical groups
- AI billing code suggestions (CPT/ICD)
- Target: 280 practices, $120K MRR

### Phase 4–5 — Dominate (Years 4–5, 2028–2029)
